00:00:48.410 --> 00:00:51.059
GRANT FAULKNER: Thanks, David.

00:00:51.059 --> 00:00:52.100
Thanks so much, everyone.

00:00:52.100 --> 00:00:53.060
Thanks for coming.

00:00:53.060 --> 00:00:54.400
