00:53:43.100 --> 00:53:44.630
like, how to write
great suspense,

00:53:44.630 --> 00:53:47.320
how to rate a great plot,
how to write great dialogue.

00:53:47.320 --> 00:53:50.770
There are hundreds of
books on that subject.

00:53:50.770 --> 00:53:52.550
And they all matter,
like writing craft

00:53:52.550 --> 00:53:54.680
does matter to
writing a good story.

00:53:54.680 --> 00:53:58.220
But I think what matters more
than that is a story where

00:53:58.220 --> 00:54:01.220
the author makes him or
herself vulnerable on the page

00:54:01.220 --> 00:54:03.550
and really connects with
the reader heart to heart.

00:54:03.550 --> 00:54:05.300
And so it's that heart
to heart connection

00:54:05.300 --> 00:54:07.644
about a story that
you can relate to

00:54:07.644 --> 00:54:09.560
and that really gives
you meaning in your life

00:54:09.560 --> 00:54:10.772
that makes that novel great.

00:54:10.772 --> 00:54:12.230
And it's great in
your mind, right?

00:54:12.230 --> 00:54:13.200
That's all that matters.

00:54:13.200 --> 00:54:14.783
It doesn't have to
be considered great

00:54:14.783 --> 00:54:18.317
by, whatever, a whole panel
of judges or something.

00:54:18.317 --> 00:54:19.400
So that's my short answer.

00:54:19.400 --> 00:54:20.840
