novels ever written, too.

00:54:56.960 --> 00:54:59.560
It's really wonderful novel.

00:54:59.560 --> 00:55:01.180
ANTHONY FRANCIS: So, oh.

00:55:01.180 --> 00:55:04.000
Let's see.

00:55:04.000 --> 00:55:06.766
So my-- I'm going to
steal someone else's--

00:55:06.766 --> 00:55:08.140
I don't remember
who to attribute

00:55:08.140 --> 00:55:11.230
